title: The Superfest East, Live in Brooklyn Edition
description:
Culturefest joins the Political Gabfest and Hang Up and Listen, onstage at the Music Hall of Williamsburg with emcee Dan Kois, for a blockbuster show in front of a live audience.
Show notes at www.slate.com/culturefest.
